  Art on the House. This is the best admission deal for exploring the Tampa
  Museum of Arts exhibitions. During Art on the House\, admission prices ch
 ange to pay-as-you-will\, and visitors can choose whatever admission price
  they want to pay. Choose 5 or choose 20\, this is a great way to cool off
  and see the museum after work! \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/
